DCterms XML Schema XML Schema for http://purl.org/dc/terms/ namespace Created 2008-02-11 Created by Tim Cole (t-cole3@uiuc.edu) Tom Habing (thabing@uiuc.edu) Jane Hunter (jane@dstc.edu.au) Pete Johnston (p.johnston@ukoln.ac.uk), Carl Lagoze (lagoze@cs.cornell.edu) This schema declares XML elements for the DC elements and DC element refinements from the http://purl.org/dc/terms/ namespace.
